title: E B Express Provisions Recalls Ineligible Canned Pork and Beef Bean Stew Products Imported From Brazil
summary: WASHINGTON, July 26, 2023 – E B Express Provisions, a distributor and importer of record located in Newark, N.J. is recalling approximately 622 pounds of the pork and beef bean stew products that were imported from an establishment in Brazil that is not eligible to...
impacted_products: •	430g cans containing “Anglo Feijoada Pronta para servir”.
•	430g cans containing “Bordon Feijoada PRONTO PARA SERVIR”
